sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant S as Staff/CS
  participant W as Web App
  participant A as API
  participant E as EventDB
  participant P as Projector
  participant R as Read Model

  S->>W: Create class schedule
  W->>A: POST class.schedule.created
  A->>E: append class.schedule.created
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: upsert rm_class_availability

  S->>W: Book seat for member
  W->>A: POST class.booking.created
  A->>R: validate seat availability
  A->>E: append class.booking.created
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: decrement seats / update booking list

  S->>W: Cancel booking
  W->>A: POST class.booking.cancelled
  A->>E: append class.booking.cancelled
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: increment seats / update booking list

  S->>W: Mark attendance
  W->>A: POST class.attendance.confirmed
  A->>E: append class.attendance.confirmed
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: finalize class participation
